<subSubSection lastPageId="7" lastPageNumber="50" pageId="6" pageNumber="49" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1436,1831,2000]" pageId="6" pageNumber="49">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,267,1868,1892]" pageId="6" pageNumber="49">Remarks.</emphasis>
This species is rarely reported. For a long time it was known only from its 
<typeStatus box="[1136,1184,1869,1893]" pageId="6" pageNumber="49">type</typeStatus>
locality (
<collectingCountry box="[1293,1358,1868,1892]" name="South Africa" pageId="6" pageNumber="49">Natal</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry name="South Africa" pageId="6" pageNumber="49">South Africa</collectingCountry>
) but 
<bibRefCitation author="Chan" box="[340,563,1903,1927]" pageId="6" pageNumber="49" refString="Chan, T. - Y. &amp; Yu, H. P. (1995) The rare lobster genus Palinustus A. Milne Edwards, 1880 (Decapoda, Palinuridae), with description of a new species. Journal of Crustacean Biology, 15 (2), 376 - 394." type="journal article" year="1995">
Chan &amp; Yu (
<number box="[497,555,1903,1927]" pageId="6" pageNumber="49" value="1995.0">1995</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
and Richer de Forges &amp; Laboute (
<number box="[988,1046,1903,1927]" pageId="6" pageNumber="49" value="1995.0">1995</number>
) have indicated that it is widely distributed in the Indo-west Pacific. In 
<collectingCountry box="[655,851,1940,1964]" name="French Polynesia" pageId="6" pageNumber="49">French Polynesia</collectingCountry>
it was already reported from the 
<taxonomicName box="[1245,1348,1941,1964]" class="Malacostraca" family="Dynomenidae" genus="Metadynomene" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="6" pageNumber="60" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tuamotu">Tuamotu</taxonomicName>
, 
<quantity box="[1362,1436,1940,1964]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.5" pageId="6" pageNumber="49" unit="m" value="250.0">250 m</quantity>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Poupin" box="[206,470,1976,2000]" pageId="6" pageNumber="49" refString="Poupin, J. (1996) Atlas des crustaces marins profonds de Polynesie francaise. Recoltes du navire Marara, 1986 / 1996. Rapport Scientifique du Service Mixte de Surveillance Radiologique et Biologique, SMSRB, 59 pp., pls. 1 - 20. [http: // hal. archivesouvertes. fr / hal- 00411280]" type="book chapter" year="1996" yearSuffix="f">
Poupin 
<number box="[294,354,1976,2000]" pageId="6" pageNumber="49" value="1996.0">1996</number>
: 
<number box="[365,395,1976,2000]" pageId="6" pageNumber="49" value="14.0">14</number>
, pl. 
<number box="[443,458,1976,2000]" pageId="6" pageNumber="49" value="6.0">6</number>
f
</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<caption httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/282842/files/figure.png" pageId="7" pageNumber="50" targetBox="[151,1435,193,1477]" targetPageId="7">
