<paragraph blockId="7.[151,1436,1597,1765]" pageId="7" pageNumber="50">
<taxonomicName box="[151,252,1597,1621]" class="Malacostraca" family="Palinuridae" genus="Puerulus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="7" pageNumber="50" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[151,252,1597,1621]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="50">Puerulus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
sp. Chan 
<emphasis box="[364,420,1597,1621]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="50">et al.</emphasis>
(in press). Stn 
<number box="[590,620,1597,1621]" pageId="7" pageNumber="50" value="36.0">36</number>
, Eiao, 
<quantity box="[697,768,1597,1621]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.27" pageId="7" pageNumber="50" unit="m" value="227.0">227 m</quantity>
(
<figureCitation box="[783,851,1597,1621]" captionStart="FIGURE 4" captionStartId="7.[151,250,1499,1522]" captionTargetBox="[151,1435,193,1477]" captionTargetId="figure@7.[151,1436,193,1478]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURE 4. Lobsters photographed with ROV Super Achille: a) Enoplometopus crosnieri Chan &amp; Yu, 1998, stn 16, Fatu Hiva, 204 m; b) Palinustus unicornutus Berry, 1979, stn 37, Eiao, 242 m; c – d) Puerulus sp. Chan et al. (in press), stn 36, Eiao, 227 m." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/282842/files/figure.png" pageId="7" pageNumber="50">
Fig. 
<number box="[836,851,1597,1621]" pageId="7" pageNumber="50" value="4.0">4</number>
</figureCitation>
c–d). R/V 
<taxonomicName authority="H.Karst." authorityName="H.Karst." box="[967,1054,1598,1621]" class="Liliopsida" family="Arecaceae" genus="Marara" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Arecales" pageId="7" pageNumber="50" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[967,1054,1598,1621]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="50">Marara</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, trap, Tahuata, 
<quantity box="[1228,1352,1597,1621]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.75" metricValueMax="4.3" metricValueMin="3.2" pageId="7" pageNumber="50" unit="m" value="375.0" valueMax="430.0" valueMin="320.0">
320– 
<specimenCount box="[1285,1352,1597,1621]" pageId="7" pageNumber="50" type="generic">430m</specimenCount>
</quantity>
. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,260,1633,1657]" pageId="7" pageNumber="50">Remarks</emphasis>
. This species has been previously reported from the Marquesas as 
<taxonomicName authority="Bate, 1888" authorityName="Bate" authorityYear="1888" box="[1057,1436,1633,1657]" class="Malacostraca" family="Palinuridae" genus="Puerulus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="7" pageNumber="50" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="angulatus">
<emphasis box="[1057,1281,1633,1657]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="50">Puerulus angulatus</emphasis>
(Bate, 
<number box="[1371,1428,1633,1657]" pageId="7" pageNumber="50" value="1888.0">1888</number>
)
</taxonomicName>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Poupin" box="[206,502,1669,1693]" pageId="7" pageNumber="50" refString="Poupin, J. (1996) Atlas des crustaces marins profonds de Polynesie francaise. Recoltes du navire Marara, 1986 / 1996. Rapport Scientifique du Service Mixte de Surveillance Radiologique et Biologique, SMSRB, 59 pp., pls. 1 - 20. [http: // hal. archivesouvertes. fr / hal- 00411280]" type="book chapter" year="1996" yearSuffix="g">
Poupin 
<number box="[301,361,1669,1693]" pageId="7" pageNumber="50" value="1996.0">1996</number>
: 
<number box="[379,409,1669,1693]" pageId="7" pageNumber="50" value="14.0">14</number>
, pl. 
<quantity box="[471,502,1669,1693]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="kg" metricValue="6.0" pageId="7" pageNumber="50" unit="g" value="6.0">6g</quantity>
</bibRefCitation>
). A morphological re-examination coupled with 
<collectionCode LSID="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:15536" box="[1090,1151,1669,1693]" httpUri="http://biocol.org/urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:15536" name="Department of Natural Resources, Environment, The Arts and Sport" pageId="7" pageNumber="50">DNA</collectionCode>
sequencing has shown, however, that the Marquesan specimens belong to a new species nested within the 
<taxonomicName box="[1211,1436,1705,1729]" class="Malacostraca" family="Palinuridae" genus="Puerulus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="7" pageNumber="50" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="angulatus">
<emphasis box="[1211,1436,1705,1729]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="50">Puerulus angulatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
complex of species (Chan 
<emphasis box="[496,552,1741,1765]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="50">et al.</emphasis>
in press)
</paragraph>
